      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-maintained throughout its life. The engine and transmission run smoothly, and the interior is clean with only minor signs of use. While there are a few small cosmetic blemishes on the exterior, it remains a reliable and attractive option for a daily driver. You can expect a solid driving experience with no major repairs needed in the near future.",
